{"questionId":"14661692","questionHtml":"<p>Hence, find the Maclaurin series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><msup><mi>cos</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></msup></math>,&nbsp;up to and including the term in&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mn>24</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p>attempt to substitute series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>into series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>Award<strong> (M0) </strong>for substituting the Maclaurin series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;into the Maclaurin series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup></math>.</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mstyle></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo> </mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></msup></math></strong></em></p>\n<p>attempt to find the Maclaurin series for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp;OR&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>&nbsp; (M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo><mo>;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>…</mo></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msup><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mrow><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> A1&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; 